    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps">Sichardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1905" key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Roffrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendarii</rs> nostri, tibi <name
                            ref="Maio">Maioni</name> filio <name ref="Tassilo">Tassilonis</name>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/3418" key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"><rs
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >curtem</rs> in loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                                key="#Villages/settlements #Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                                >Folianense</placeName></geogName> cum <rs key="#Slave">servis et
                            ancillis</rs> et omnibus pertinentiis suis, que fuit tua et per meritum
                        culpe tuę <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >ad sacrum palatium evenit</rs> atque a bone memorie domino et genitore
                        nostro <persName ref="#people/3618" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Maioni</persName> filio <persName ref="#people/3619"
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">Magiperti</persName> per preceptum
                        concesse fuit, sed pro quo iam dictus Maio filius Magiperti extra provinciam
                        nostram <placeName ref="#places/2350" key="#Cities">Neapolim</placeName>
                        fugiit, predictam curtem <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_criminals/political_traitors"
                            >ad nostrum palatium denuo rediit</rs>, ideo ipsa curtem in integrum cum
                        servis et ancillis et omnibus pertinentiis suis tibi prephato Maioni
                        concessemus, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum
                        roboreum preceptum tu et heredes tui sepe dictam curtem cum pertinentiæ suę,
                        ut iam ea tenuisti, habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus ipsa possideatis.
                        Quod vero preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName ref="#people/3465" key="#Notary">Audoaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Atum &lt;sic> <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName> secundo anno, mense decembrio,
                        quinta decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
